## 📂 Directory Overview

```
mabarana-group-api-servies/
├── app.js                  ← Fastify app builder
├── server.js               ← Server entry point
├── config/                 ← Configuration files
├── middleware/             ← Auth & error handling middleware
├── plugins/                ← Fastify plugins (3rd party integrations)
├── routes/                 ← API route modules (12 domains)
├── utils/                  ← Helper & utility functions
├── prisma/                 ← Database schema & migrations
├── templates/              ← HTML email templates
├── docs/                   ← API documentation markdown files
├── scripts/                ← Utility scripts
└── logs/                   ← Runtime log files (auto-generated)
```

---

## 📂 config/

Database connection, environment validation, Firebase config.

```
config/
├── dbConnect.js        ← Prisma DB connection helper
├── env.schema.js       ← Zod schema for environment variable validation
└── firebase.js         ← Firebase Admin SDK initialization
```

---

## 📂 middleware/

Global middleware — authentication, authorization, error handling.

```
middleware/
├── authMiddleware.js           ← JWT auth + role-based access (ADMIN, MANAGER, CASHIER)
├── customerAuthMiddleware.js   ← Customer-specific JWT authentication
└── errorHandler.js             ← Global error handler + 404 handler
```

---

## 📂 plugins/

Fastify plugin registrations (encapsulated 3rd party integrations).

```
plugins/
├── axios.js            ← fastify-axios plugin (HTTP client)
├── cookie.js           ← @fastify/cookie plugin
├── cors.js             ← @fastify/cors plugin (cross-origin settings)
├── cron.js             ← node-cron setup (scheduled jobs)
├── multipart.js        ← @fastify/multipart (file uploads)
├── nodemailer.js       ← fastify-nodemailer (email sending)
├── prisma.js           ← Prisma client plugin (DB decorator)
├── rateLimiting.js     ← @fastify/rate-limit plugin
├── requestLogger.js    ← HTTP request logging plugin
├── static.js           ← @fastify/static (serve static files)
└── swagger.js          ← @fastify/swagger + swagger-ui (API docs)
```

---

## 📂 routes/

Main API business logic. සෑම module එකකම **3 files** ඇත:

| File | භූමිකාව |
|------|---------|
| [index.js](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-api-servies/routes/users/index.js) | Route definitions + middleware binding |
| [handler.js](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-api-servies/routes/users/handler.js) | Business logic (controller functions) |
| [schema.js](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-api-servies/config/env.schema.js) | Zod / JSON schemas for request validation |

### Route Modules & API Prefixes

| Module | API Prefix | විස්තරය |
|--------|-----------|---------|
| `users/` | `/api/users` | Admin/Manager/Cashier user management, login, password reset |
| `customer/` | `/api/customers` | Customer registration, login, OTP, profile |
| `merchant/` | `/api/merchants` | Merchant CRUD operations |
| `branch/` | `/api/branches` | Branch management under merchants |
| `organization/` | `/api/organizations` | Organization management |
| `subscription/` | `/api/subscriptions` | Subscription plans, payments, renewals |
| `discount/` | `/api/discounts` | Discount & coupon management |
| `banner/` | `/api/banners` | Banner image management |
| `notification/` | `/api/notifications` | Push & in-app notifications |
| `payment/` | `/api/payment` | Payment processing integration |
| `upload/` | `/api/upload` | File upload to Firebase Storage |
| `metrics/` | `/api/metrics` | System/business metrics |

---

## 📂 utils/

Reusable helper functions used across the entire app.

```
utils/
├── cache.js                    ← LRU cache setup
├── cacheInvalidation.js        ← Cache invalidation helpers
├── cronJobs.js                 ← Background scheduled job logic
├── email.js                    ← Email sending helpers (uses templates)
├── errors.js                   ← Custom error class definitions
├── generateCustomerTokens.js   ← JWT token generation for customers
├── generateReferralCode.js     ← Referral code generator
├── generateTokens.js           ← JWT token generation for users
├── notificationHelper.js       ← Push notification helpers (Firebase FCM)
├── otpUtils.js                 ← OTP generation & verification
├── payment.js                  ← Payment gateway helper functions
├── systemInfo.js               ← OS/system info for health endpoint
└── uploadToFirebase.js         ← Firebase Storage upload logic
```

