## 🔄 Request Flow

```
Client Request
      ↓
  server.js          (HTTP server start)
      ↓
  app.js             (Fastify instance + plugin/route registration)
      ↓
  plugins/           (cors, rate-limit, auth cookies, swagger...)
      ↓
  middleware/        (JWT authentication, role authorization)
      ↓
  routes/*/index.js  (Route matching)
      ↓
  routes/*/handler.js (Business logic)
      ↓
  utils/ + prisma    (DB queries, emails, notifications...)
      ↓
  Response → Client
```

---

## 🛡️ Auth Roles

| Role | Access |
|------|--------|
| `ADMIN` | Full system access |
| `MANAGER` | Merchant/branch/user management |
| `CASHIER` | Limited operational access |
| `CUSTOMER` | Customer-facing API (separate JWT flow) |
